  "body": "Goal: make the \"blsync\" tool capable of serving the same REST API that it requires\r\nStatus: implemented, needs some cleanup before review\r\n\r\nNote: this does not mean implementing all endpoints defined by the CL API specs as this would be impossible based on a light sync of the beacon chain; the goal is to be able to propagate CL light client data between CL light clients in the same format they consume when connected to a full beacon node.\r\n\r\nRelevant branch:\r\n\r\n- https://github.com/zsfelfoldi/go-ethereum/tree/blsync-server\r\n",
